SSG2 might be my most played app game of all time. It is fun, addictive, challenging, and packed with content. SSG3 retains some of these qualities but there is significantly less content unless you‚Äôre paying for premium. In addition to this, the more aggressive attempts to monetize the game (while I understand that they‚Äôre necessary) make collecting hats and costumes much less fun and make attempting difficult courses or challenges very frustrating. 

Put simply, the best parts of this game are more of the same from SSG2, while the worst parts will frustrate me enough to discourage me from playing at all. Get SSG2 and think of this game as additional content in the event that you want more.
